hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 写出 $p=1$ 和 $p=3$ 时的 $\mathcal{V}$：
$$\mathcal{V}_{1\bar{1}}=-2\frac{\Gamma(\tfrac{7-1}2)}{4\pi^{(9-1)/2}}\,(2\kappa_{10}^2T_1^2)L^{-6},\quad
\mathcal{V}_{3\bar{3}}=-2\frac{\Gamma(\tfrac{7-3}2)}{4\pi^{(9-3)/2}}\,(2\kappa_{10}^2T_3^2)L^{-4}$$
2. 计算Gamma函数和$\pi$的幂次：
$\Gamma(3)=2$, $(9-1)/2=4\Rightarrow\pi^4$; $\Gamma(2)=1$, $(9-3)/2=3\Rightarrow\pi^3$.
3. 构造比值：
$$\mathcal{R}=\frac{\mathcal{V}_{1\bar{1}}}{\mathcal{V}_{3\bar{3}}}
=\frac{\tfrac{2}{4\pi^4}\,2\kappa_{10}^2T_1^2\,L^{-6}}
{\tfrac{1}{4\pi^3}\,2\kappa_{10}^2T_3^2\,L^{-4}}
=\frac{2/(4\pi^4)}{1/(4\pi^3)}\frac{T_1^2}{T_3^2}L^{-2}
=\frac{2}{\pi}\frac{T_1^2}{T_3^2}\frac1{L^2}$$
4. 代入张力：
$$T_p=\frac1{g_s(2\pi)^p(\alpha')^{(p+1)/2}}\;\Longrightarrow\;
\frac{T_1}{T_3}
=\frac{1/(2\pi g_s\alpha')}{1/(8\pi^3g_s(\alpha')^2)}
=4\pi^2\,\alpha'\,,\;
\Bigl(\frac{T_1}{T_3}\Bigr)^2=16\pi^4(\alpha')^2$$
5. 因此
$$\mathcal{R}=\frac{2}{\pi}\,16\pi^4(\alpha')^2\,\frac1{L^2}
=32\pi^3\frac{(\alpha')^2}{L^2}$$
